@NODE SHORTCUTS "Appendix A: Keyboard Shortcuts"

@{b}General Shortcuts@{ub}

All of these short cuts require you to hold down the RIGHT Amiga key.

	Key	Operation

	 N	Clear shapes list
	 O	Load Image
	 A	Display About Requester
	0-9	Save shape in specified format
	 I	Iconify ShapeZ
	 Q	Quit ShapeZ
	 K	Configure ShapeZ

@{b}Window Shortcuts@{ub}

All of these short cuts require you to hold down the RIGHT Amiga key.

	Key	Operation

	 S	Snap Shot Window Positions for start-up
	 R	Restore Snapshot
	 E	Open Editor
	 Z	Open Zoom window
	 H 	Open Help window
	 P	Open Palette window
	 T	Open Animation window
	 U	Open Utilties window
	 D	Open Viewing window
	 
@{b}Shape Shortcuts@{ub}

All of these short cuts require you to hold down the RIGHT Amiga key.

	Key	Operation

	 F	Goto first shape in list
	 L	Goto last shape in list
	 ,	Goto previous shape
	 . 	Goto next shape
	 G	Goto to a shape you specify
	 +	Add shape
	 C	Copy shape
	 V	Past shape
	 X	Cut shape	

@{b}Editor Only Shortcuts@{ub}

These shortcuts are only available from the editor window, and do not
require you to hold down any other keys. If you do so, you may activate
a meun short-cut!

	Key	Operation

	 r	Restore Brush
	 x	Flip Shape Horizontally
	 y	Flip Shape Vertically
	 w	Rotate Shape
	 s	Resize Shape
	 +	Zoom in
	 - 	Zoom out

@ENDNODE SHORTCUTS

